<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 19 at 4:48AM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...ICY SPOTS POSSIBLE ON UNTREATED SURFACES THIS MORNING...
The combination of snow, ice and rain from yesterday into last
night and below freezing temperatures may result in some icy spots
on untreated surfaces early this morning. Drivers are urged to
use caution this morning and be aware for potential slippery
travel conditions.</description>
